jltl2dstar

Class SafrasAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2dstar.SafrasAlgorithm

  • public class SafrasAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which calculates the transition function of Safra's algorithm. You have to provide at least the final states of the NBA, the other values have to be set, if the corresponding option is set.

      Safra tree visitor that creates a new child node if the label of the node and the set of final states in the NBA intersect.

      A Safra tree visitor that checks if all the successor states in the NBA of the label are accepting.
